@startuml level3_pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 3 — Sequential Pipeline**\n//Fixed sequential order, no review, no evaluation//

|#E3F2FD|Stage 1|
start
:<<Engagement Manager>>\n**qwen3:8b** (Ollama)\n\nDecompose question\ninto workstreams;
:Output: Analysis Plan;

|#E8F5E9|Stage 2|
:<<Market Researcher>>\n**qwen3:14b** (Ollama)\n\nAnalyze market landscape;
:Output: Market Analysis;

|#FFF3E0|Stage 3|
:<<Financial Analyst>>\n**deepseek-r1:14b** (Ollama)\n\nModel financials & projections;
:Output: Financial Analysis;

|#FFEBEE|Stage 4|
:<<Risk Analyst>>\n**qwen3:14b** (Ollama)\n\nIdentify & assess risks;
:Output: Risk Matrix;

|#F3E5F5|Stage 5|
:<<Strategy Consultant>>\n**qwen3:32b** (Ollama)\n\nSynthesize all inputs\ninto final recommendation;
:Output: Consulting Report;
stop

note right
  **Pipeline characteristics:**
  * Sequential pipeline, each agent runs once
  * No revision capability
  * No evaluator stage
  * Cumulative data routing
  * 5 agents, all via Ollama
end note

@enduml
